 * `<source>` and `<object>` tags. Attribute values can be double-quoted, single-quoted
 * or unquoted.
 *
 * Groups:
 * 1. `<` character
 * 2. the tag name (e.g. `img`, `IMG`, `video`)
 * 3. content between tag name and attribute name (other attributes, whitespace)
 * 4. the attribute name (`src` or `data`)
 * 5. the `=` sign (possibly surrounded by whitespace)
 * 6. the full attribute value token (including quotes if present)
 * 7. the value if double-quoted
 * 8. the value if single-quoted
 * 9. the value if unquoted
 */
